@startuml istio-timeline
title Istio — Sidecar → Ambient (linha do tempo aproximada)

left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor transparent

rectangle "2017–2018\nIstio 0.x → 1.0\nSidecar é o único modelo" as t1
rectangle "set/2022\nAmbient Mesh\nanunciado" as t2
rectangle "meados 2023\nIstio 1.18\nAmbient em alpha" as t3
rectangle "2024\nIstio 1.22\nAmbient em beta" as t4
rectangle "nov/2024\nIstio 1.24\nAmbient GA" as t5

t1 -right-> t2
t2 -right-> t3
t3 -right-> t4
t4 -right-> t5

note bottom of t5
  Este projeto roda Istio 1.30.2
  (ver istio-configmap-tracing-patch.yaml)
  — já bem depois do GA do Ambient.
end note

@enduml
